院\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　 111　　年　　10　　月　　26　　日\r\n                           檢察官   陳寧君","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TYDM/111%2c%e5%a3%a2%e7%b0%a1%2c2163%2c20221111%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TYDM,111,壢簡,2163,20221111,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"壢簡","JNO":"2163","JDATE":"20221111","JTITLE":"竊盜"}